# west workspace artifacts — a ZMK user-config repo must contain only
# config/, build.yaml and .github/. The workspace and its imported projects
# are created by `west init`/`west update` in CI and must never be committed,
# or `west init` aborts with "already initialized".
.west/
zmk/
zephyr/
modules/
prospector-touch-zmk-module/

# build output
build/
*.uf2
*.hex
*.bin
